Tasks.Name: Breed females AI 10-14 hours after standing heat.
Turn clean up bulls in with females
Inject $PG to all females not detected in heat
Breed females AI 10-14 hours if showing standing heat

Protocols.Name: 1 Injection Prostaglandin (prior estrus detection)
Protocols.Description:
Animal must be cycling (CL present) & between day 5 - 17 after estrus to respond to each PG injection.

This program will not work if animal is anestrous or prepubertal.

If all animals are cycling, expect 20 - 25% to show heat prior to PG injection.

Interval from PG to estrus variable, but most animals will exhibit estrus 36 - 96 hrs after PG injection.

Low estrus detection rates and the proportion of females cycling often limit pregnancy rates.

A low cost, low risk sytem but also low synchrony.

Immediate addition of clean-up bulls could lead to questions about parentage.

Protocols.Name: 1 Injection Prostaglandin (no prior estrus detection)
Protocols.Description:
Animal must be cycling (CL present) & between day 5 - 17 after estrus to respond to each PG injection. 

This program will not work if animal is anestrous or prepubertal.

If all animals are cycling, expect no more than 70 - 75% to exhibit estrus.

Interval from PG to estrus variable, but most animals will exhibit estrus 36 - 96 hrs after PG injection.

Low estrus detection rates and the proportion of females cycling often limit pregnancy rates.

Immediate addition of clean-up bulls could lead to questions about parentage.

Protocols.Name: 2 Injection Prostaglandin (no prior estrus detection)
Protocols.Description:
Animal must be cycling (CL present) & between day 5 - 17 after estrus to respond to each PG injection. 

This program will not work if animal is anestrous or prepubertal.

If all animals are cycling, the majority should respond to second PG injection.

Interval from PG to estrus variable, but most animals will exhibit estrus 36 - 96 hrs after PG injection.

Low estrus detection rates and the proportion of females cycling often limit pregnancy rates.

Interval between PG injections could range from 11 to 14 days, however 14 days provides best results.

Immediate addition of clean-up bulls could lead to questions about parentage.

Injections.
